{"tid":1225875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月2日之前記得登記做選民，叫埋身邊朋友去登記","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:53:59.000Z","uid":5539,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21ecec3f6f88b85fcf4225f769a1e689cf157227","tid":1225875,"uid":5539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"提提大家得返半個月炸，我知呢到大部分人都登記左，但係你身邊ge 人都未架<br />\n仲有班00後，有d 都18,19歲，係時候要出黎履行返公民責任，登記選民！就快夠18歲果班記得拎身份證果時順便登記埋呀！！<br />\n<br />\n登記好簡單<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">選民登記資格</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 年滿18歲<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港永久性居民<br />\n<br />\n3. 通常在港居住<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n索取及填寫表格<br />\n<br />\n只要符合以上選民資格，就可以立即填寫「地方選區選民新登記申請表」(REO-1)，就可以在立法會和區議會選舉中投票，選出可以代表自己的議會代表。 <br />\n<br />\n1. 網上索取「地方選區選民新登記申請表」(REO-1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=b3f8e8e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 傳真 (致電熱線2891 1001)<br />\n<br />\n3. 各區民政事務處<br />\n<br />\n4. 公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<br />\n5. 選舉事務處 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遞交表格方法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n市民可以選擇以下5種方法遞交表格。<br />\n<br />\n1. 郵寄至 <span style=\"color: gold;\">九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 傳真至 2891 1180<br />\n<br />\n3. 掃瞄表格後電郵至 form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n4. 掃瞄表格/填寫電子表格後上載至選舉事務處的電子表格上載平台<br />\n<br />\n5. 若持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證(個人)證書，亦可使用香港政府一站通作網上登記<br />\n<br />\n一定一定要登記！！！每一票都好重要！！<br />\n今次政府咁強硬推修例係因為建制派議員係立法會佔過半數先可以控制議會，下一屆必須令更多泛民或獨立人士入去，先可以避免再有一次反送中嘅惡夢，令我地年輕人唔洗再賭上前程去勇武抗爭。好簡單，如果送到過半泛民入去，你諗下政府就算想推，但都唔夠自己友係立會，佢仲會唔會好似今次咁強硬推，經過今次反送中之後冇人係鬼，唔好再分化民主派，呢場係持久戰，有票先有話事權！！老套講句大家團結一致，一條心就事成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">616 維園見</span></span>"},{"pid":"d08b5d8e4b33d818fefcd6bc6cc8ef70e245c50d","tid":1225875,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民建聯 898"},{"pid":"43d7ce3001223f38bb2956bad718ba2c774b1e7b","tid":1225875,"uid":53829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"我過左改地址嗰時間喎,有冇辦法呀"},{"pid":"603abb5076e7834df65292ab32832488756f6efb","tid":1225875,"uid":111909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"推 票債票償<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78093df8b7863750d525867fa26b4b74da0bec9","tid":1225875,"uid":5539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d7ce3001223f38bb2956bad718ba2c774b1e7b","tid":1225875,"uid":53829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"我過左改地址嗰時間喎,有冇辦法呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"已登記的選民如更改住址或個人資料須盡快通知選舉事務處。如你在6月2日（區議會選舉年）或4月2日（非區議會選舉年）或之前作出有關申報，你在該年正式選民登記冊上的資料將會獲更新。如你希望更改登記資料（例如姓名、住址或聯絡電話），你必須填寫「地方選區選民更改登記資料申請表」（REO-2）。<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-2(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-2%28C%29.pdf&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=9547dc98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-2(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n請注意，選民在提出更改登記住址申請時須同時提交住址證明。<br />\n<br />\n最好打去問下"},{"pid":"cff368464b603e2da3223bc6f8408824efa33258","tid":1225875,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"仍需求大量選民登記表格聽日派<br />\n大家可以今晚係美孚交低選民登記表比我或者聽日自發咁去派<br />\n<br />\n我會於維園入口set站派表<br />\n需要大家沿路同於終點繼續派<br />\n感激大家！ <br />\n<br />\n選民登記表格link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=168355b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\nTg group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=d362f105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DFZtbBYpgyLP_AFD8epM3A</a>"},{"pid":"56cdf0a7ec257ade90e57b091761d2b88a96e1bd","tid":1225875,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8aead9e889807cf4bcd1b1fffaef8d838bbee2","tid":1225875,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"fb30ec8d5feda32f870ff8c61fb69ac606c8feb1","tid":1225875,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"外國讀書算唔算通常居住香港"},{"pid":"0f8badbe89b924aae600ebbf5f02a3cd4f2ca8b8","tid":1225875,"uid":5539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"聽日遊行完要主推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0730cd43eebd1b5655f1f7bd0d1153a06f42ca","tid":1225875,"uid":5539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"遊行完啦，大家返屋企得閒就填下表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets